{ A cunning move order, trying to create threats on the c-file quickly. } 14.
b3
{ Smart. We get ready to develop our bishop to b2 before placing our knight on c3. Next up our plan is very simple - just develop and stabilize the centre, after which our superior structure will give us a slight edge. }
