{ Natural but does not work here.   15...Ra8  16.Nbd2  transposes to14...Re8. }
16. dxe5 Bxe3 17. exf6
{ Here Black would like to capture a knight on d2, but we played Re1 instead of Nbd2 meaning there is nothing to capture! }
17... Ba7 18. fxg7
{ White has won a pawn and although the bishop pair gives Black some compensation it really isn't close to enough. }
