17... Qe7 { The only move! } 18. Qh5 h6
{ Again there follows a tactical sequence which is very common for the Arkhangelsk. Pay close attention! }
19. Nxf7 Rxf7 20. Bxf7+ Qxf7 21. Qxf7+ Kxf7 22. d5
{ Now we win a piece, leaving us an exchange up in the ending. } 22... Bxe3 23.
dxc6 { The best way for Black to play an exchange down is } 23... Bd4 24. cxb7
