{ would be a rather major strategic mistake, as we can keep our bishop. } 13.
Bc2 { Black's Na5 looks strange now and we are in time to defend our centre. }
13... Re8 14. Re1 Bxe4 { ends up being nice for us } 15. Bxe4 Nxe4 16. Nxe4
