18... Kh8 { Would be a funny counter-waiting move, preparing to push ...d4. }
19. Qd2
{ Seems like a good move here though. The inclusion of Kh1 Kh8 works strongly in White's favour, as after  19...Qg6  we now have  20.g4!  without Nh3+. }
