Nh5 15. Nbd2 Bf6 16. Kh2
{ Remember this idea! We are getting ready to kick the f4-knight out with Ng1 followed by g3. }
16... Nf4 17. Ng1
{ Calmly intending to kick the knight out, after which the g1-knight can get activated again. }
17... Bg7 18. g3 Nh5 19. Ngf3
{ The black activity has evaporated. Next, we intend the interesting maneuver Nh4-f5 @@StartBracket@@as the h5-knight is hanging@@EndBracket@@, and if Black retreats to f6 then we will slowly bring pieces over to the kingside and start pushing pawns there. }
