14. Nc4
{ An excellent square for the knight, from where it attacks e5, making ...d5 very hard for Black to achieve. Without being able to push ...d5 it's very hard for Black to get activity. We can slowly develop with Bd2, and if allowed, a5 and Ba4. Later on, when circumstances allow it, we will finally push d4. But there is no hurry! }
