b4
{ The fastest way of creating play. We are not afraid of giving up a pawn if it means we will get a big initative in the centre. With an open centre the knight on h5 and pawn on f4 would look very clumsy. }
14... g5 { does not work due to the typical tactic } 15. d5 Ne7 16. Nfxe5 dxe5
17. Qxh5 { winning a pawn } *

