3... g6
{ 3...a6  4.Ba4  g6  5.c3  Nge7  or @@StartFEN@@r1bqkbnr/1ppp1ppp/p1n5/4p3/B3P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQK2R b KQkq - 1 4@@EndFEN@@  4...Nge7  5.c3  g6  , are alternative move orders simply transposing into the same line. }
