10... Nc4 { Also pretty bad for Black. } 11. Bc3 Bxc3+ 12. Nxc3 Nxb2 13. Qc1
Nc4 14. Bd3
{ One of many good moves. We are a pawn down, but the initiative is very strong. If Black castles we immediately attack the king, and if not, then increasing pressure in the centre is a good strategy. }
14... Nb6 { is a natural try, but now } 15. a4 b4 16. a5
{ gives us overwhelming compensation for the pawn. Black's pieces are simply not doing enough. }
