Nd5
{ There are simply too many threats, and Black's extra exchange is not felt at all. }
15... Qg7 16. Bd2
{ Next we can, for instance, just castle and then put a bishop on d6, or prepare Bf4 Qd2 followed by Bh6. It doesn't matter much, as Black has no counterplay whatsover and incredibly lousy coordination. }
