12... Re8 13. b4 { Intending a4, putting pressure on Black's queenside. } 13...
a5 14. Rb1 axb4 15. axb4
{ Looks fairly comfortable for us. Black's bishop is a bit strangely placed on b7, and we will be able to gain space with d4 soon. }
