10. Bg3 O-O
{ If you see O-O in this structure, for the first time you might think it looks scary for Black, but in fact it's a very common thing to do also after g5. The kingside is so limited and the g3-bishop actually more in the way than contributing to White's play, so it is relatively safe to castle short. Still, it does give us a target and even if we aren't close to mating now, there is always some potential in the future. }
