{ This is considered to be one of the main downsides of 5.d3 instead of 6.d3. Normally against the Arkhangelsk we want to push c3 and d4, but here that is no longer a tempting option, as it would lose a very important tempo. The fact that Jan Gustafsson recommends this in his Lifetime Repertoire on 1.e4 e5 is a testimony to how solid it is. }
