{ We are intending to play d4 and recapture with our knight on d4, for which the e4-pawn needs to be defended. }
7... Be7 { By far the main move. } 8. d4
{ Our idea is to increase our space advantage. A funny thing is that this position can also be reached via @@StartFEN@@r1bqkbnr/pppp1ppp/2n5/4p3/4P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQKB1R w KQkq - 2 3@@EndFEN@@  3.Bb5  a6  4.Ba4  Nf6  5.O-O  d6  6.Bxc6+  bxc6  7.Re1  Be7  8.d4  . }
