13... Nxe4 14. dxe4 a5
{ Is an interesting positional concept for Black - they lose some time, but gain a nice square on c5. }
15. b5 Nb8 16. Qb3 { Developing with tempo. } 16... Be6 17. Be3 Nd7 18. Red1
